column2: select an.ID, TID=tn.ID, Worker=c.VAL from optw.ptheta.Portland1#Assets an     join optw.ptheta.Portland1#Drive d on d.DestNodeID=an.NodeID     join optw.ptheta.Portland1#Tracts tn on d.OrigNodeID=tn.NodeID     join optw.tamass.VALS c on c.TRACTID=tn.ID where Minutes < #     and c.VARID=# -- # of people in tract     and an.ID=# order by an.ID
